  "text": "Gt-GTP ＋ R* ⇆ Gt-R* ＋ GTP (1) http://bmbreports.org BMB reports Such a reaction could result in a significant decrease in the amount of Gt available to activate PDE in the presence of excess R*. This could provide a means of photoreceptor adaptation during background illumination and/or after bleaching of significant amounts of rhodopsin [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
